Globally, the Seawater Flake Ice Machine market is projected to reach USD 1,103.1 million by 2029, growing at a CAGR of 5.8% from 2023 to 2029. This growth is driven by the expanding applications of flake ice in various industries and technological advancements enhancing machine efficiency.
